appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We’ve improved our video uploading process top to bottom, making sure a bad internet connection will not ruin your day. Videos now get a second (third, fourth.. you get it) chance to upload and we keep them safe and sound until they make it on the other side.
Last but not least, you can now create blank video tabs, name them and arrange them, give them all the love long before reaching the filming spot. Now there’s really nothing that can break your flow once you get your directors hat on.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: In our biggest update yet, Spaces now can be marked down as Not Listed, On The Market, Let Agreed, and Moved In. Last but not least, by popular demand, we made it so that users can add pre-defined video tabs with just a few taps. You can thank Adam from Paramount Properties for that one.

title: Holofy Spaces

creator: Holofy Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Holofy Spaces is a video-first sales intelligence platform that helps you generate, qualify and close more leads, faster than anyone else.

We do that by giving you the most powerful medium to generate engagement and understand customer intent: video stories.
The Holofy Spaces App lets you create, manage, and publish content, as well as understand your lead's purchase intent through the power of deep analytics.

With a tap, you can share entire asset portfolios or curate custom collections that you forward directly to your leads, embed on your website or 3rd party platforms.
descriptionShort: Market your real-estate assets and extract new levels of business intelligence.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: By popular demand, this update brings back the web link CTA. Every space can now have a custom button with a custom link attached, that can adapt to bespoke conversion funnels. Update and enjoy.

title: Holofy Spaces

creator: Holofy Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Holofy is a video-powered sales engagement platform that streamlines the entire conversion funnel for real-estate businesses that want to close more deals remotely.

Our video first experience embeds seamlessly onto your website or marketplaces such as Rightmove, Zoopla, Zillow and more. Video converts on average up to 2.5x more viewers to leads, and at a higher quality than any other digital viewing technology.

Our dedicated app enables agents to effortlessly capture critical lead metrics and interests, enabling a data-driven sales process that is exponentially more efficient.

Last but not least, leads can place remote offers for the spaces they love through fully customizable application forms with built-in payment processing. Remote offers dramatically reduce the time it takes to close a committed client, and our bidding system extracts on average 12% better yields than listings without Holofy.
descriptionShort: Video-Powered Sales Engagement Platform

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Performance optimisations and bug fixes
